1.0.0
# TalaTrivia Version File
# 
# This file contains the current version of the application.
# Format: Semantic Versioning 2.0.0 (https://semver.org/)
# 
# Valid formats:
#   - Stable releases: X.Y.Z (e.g., 1.0.0, 1.2.3, 2.0.0)
#   - Pre-releases: X.Y.Z-prerelease (e.g., 1.1.0-beta.1, 2.0.0-rc.1)
# 
# Where:
#   X = MAJOR version (breaking changes)
#   Y = MINOR version (new features, backward compatible)
#   Z = PATCH version (bug fixes, backward compatible)
# 
# Pre-release suffixes:
#   -alpha.N  : Early development, unstable
#   -beta.N   : Feature complete, testing phase
#   -rc.N     : Release candidate, ready for final testing
# 
# When updating:
#   1. Update this VERSION file
#   2. Update package.json files (root and frontend)
#   3. Update .env files (APP_VERSION variable)
#   4. Update CHANGELOG.md with changes
#   5. Commit changes in release branch
#   6. Merge to main and create git tag (e.g., v1.0.0)
#   7. Build and tag Docker images with same version
